name: Vrijraj Singh
bio: Vrijraj is a front-end developer by profession and a community champion by passion. He is an organizer for GDG Jalandhar and a Google Developers Expert for Firebase and Web Technologies. He has given 80+ talks and workshops for communities over the past 5 years. His areas of expertise are around Web, Firebase, Google Cloud Platform, and UI/UX Design. He is always eager to learn new technologies and develop solutions based on them. He enjoys mentoring people and  nurturing communities. Outside work, he is a foodie and enjoys watching YouTube videos.

name: Ashwani Kumar
bio: A member of GDG Jalandhar, student of Guru Nanak Dev University, RC Jalandhar     and pursuing BTech. CSE in 3rd year. He shows enthusiasm in the cyber security field and has been an Intern at Gurugram Cyber Cell. Speaking on InfoSec excites him more and loves to show his creativity with front-end development.

name: Batchu Thrishna
bio: She’s an Android Developer, curious to learn new things and a member at GDG Jalandhar

name: Ravi Rana
bio: Ravi Rana is a highly motivated individual, continually working for the betterment of the community. He is associated with DSC CGC for the past two years, starting as a core team member to leading it this term. He believes in learning through practical implementation and has motivated other members of the community to do so as well.

name: Yashank
bio: Yashank is a passionate and dedicated learner who loves creating solutions to real-life problems using technology. He believes strong leadership can help a community achieve greater heights. He is currently pursuing Bachelor of Technology in Computer Science and engineering from Chitkara University

name: J. Siv Ram Shastri
bio: Siv Ram is a Front-end Web Developer and a JavaScript enthusiast. Experimenting with JavaScript and exploring new frameworks is his passion. Currently experimenting with Deno and working on React. He is also an active contributor at Google Developers Group - GDG Jalandhar

name: Varsha Jaiswal
bio: Varsha is a girl with a bag full of hardwork and determination to fulfill her responsibilities. She is the Organizer and Ambassador at GDG WTM Jalandhar. Working as a Software Engineer, she has a keen interest in working on new technologies. Being a facilitator of #IamRemarkable Workshop, she always gives her best to motivate her surroundings.
